SASB.FB-RN-150a.1c;UN SDG.12.1;"Amount of water recycled or reused in cubic meters.
- recycled or reused water refers to water being sourced internally by recycling or reusing avoiding further withdrawals
- treated water (not used again by the company) does not qualify as recycled water since countries/ companies are required by regulations or environmental standards to treat wastewater before discharging it into the environment";Environment
