GRI.306.3.A;TCFD.Metrics & Targets.A.1;Total amount of waste the company discards, both hazardous and non-hazardous, in thousands of metric tons. This field excludes waste given in units of volume. This field is part of the Environmental, Social and Governance (ESG) group of fields.;Environment
