TCFD.Metrics & Targets.B.1;UN SDG.11.6;"INDUSTRAILS , BANKS, FINANCIALS, INSURANCE, UTILITY & REITS

Sulphur dioxide (SO2) emissions, if available, otherwise sulphur oxides (SOx) emissions in thousands of metric tonnes. This field provides for comparability across companies that report either SO2 or SOx, but not both. Field is populated from either of the following fields in the priority shown:

SO2 Emissions is ES008, SO2_EMISSIONS
SOx Emissions is ES079, SULPHUR_OXIDE_EMISSIONS

Field is part of Environmental, Social and Governance (ESG) group of fields.";Environment
