NOx Emissions / Revenue Passenger Miles/Km

Where:
   NOx Emissions is ES007, NOX_EMISSIONS
   Revenue Passenger Miles/Km is FS002, REV_PASS_MILES_KM

Field is part of the Environmental, Social and Governance (ESG) group of fields.";Environment
